reviewText: My five stars is for the price and fast shipping FROM Britain in an amazingly quick time.  It also reflects the quality of the product, a three disc set in perfect condition.  The movies were okay.  "Dambusters" I enjoyed the most, "Colditz" was a bit of a disapointment compared to the two season mini series I just watched but still worth the watch.  Couldn't get in to "Against the Wind".
